net.smartcosmos.model.event

Interface IEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDomainResource<IEvent>, IMoniker, IUrnNamespace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Event

    public interface IEvent
extends IDomainResource<IEvent>
    Flexible mechanism for capturing user interactions with the platform. The source field contains JSON values that correlate with the specific EventType. For example, if the event is EventType.ObjectAccessed, then the getSource() will contain the JsonGenerationView.Standard serialization of the IObject that was accessed.
